    "Reason : 1 - The proposal, due to the inappropriate position and design of the hip to gable conversion and the excessive size and scale of the rear roof dormer, would result in bulky, incongruous and unsympathetic additions to the host property, which would unbalance the pair of semi-detached houses, and appear out of character with the general street scene. This would be contrary to Local Plan Policies CC1 (Context and Character), CC2 (Urban Design and Architecture), SC7 (Residential Extensions and Alterations) and the Character, Sustainability and Design Codes SPD."
